@david: I'm taking a look at this right now.<br> @david: You need to close the header component before trying to add the sidebar component.<br> @david: You have:<br>```<Header
callback={props.setSidebar}
>
{props.sidebarVisible && <Sidebar
markers={props.filteredMarkers}
callback={clickList}
filter={props.filterList}
markerOpen={props.markerOpen}
setMarkerOpen={props.onMarkerOpen}
/>}
</Header>```<br>and it should be:<br>```<Header
callback={props.setSidebar}
/>
{props.sidebarVisible && <Sidebar
markers={props.filteredMarkers}
callback={clickList}
filter={props.filterList}
markerOpen={props.markerOpen}
setMarkerOpen={props.onMarkerOpen}
/>}```<br> @chrisrb83: ahh yes of course. thank you for pointing that out!
